      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_KFEFt3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Diamond Certification: Your Complete Guide to Choosing Ethically Certified Diamonds</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_3ggfwT": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When it comes to purchasing a diamond, whether it’s for an engagement ring, a milestone celebration, or a personal investment, one factor outweighs all others — diamond certification. Certification is what transforms a sparkling stone into a verified symbol of authenticity, quality, and trust.</p><p>In today’s era of conscious luxury and ethical craftsmanship, certification is not just about value — it’s about transparency. For Indian consumers, especially those choosing<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond jewellery</span></a>, understanding certification has become an essential step toward making an informed and responsible purchase.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Is Diamond Certification?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Is Diamond Certification?</h2><p>A diamond certification is an official document issued by an independent gemological laboratory that evaluates and grades the diamond’s characteristics. These characteristics include the 4Cs — cut, color, clarity, and carat weight — along with symmetry, fluorescence, and polish.</p><p>Certification provides buyers with an unbiased assessment of a diamond’s quality, ensuring that what you pay for truly matches what you receive. Reputable laboratories such as the Gemological Institute of America (GIA), and the International Gemological Institute (IGI).</p><p>For<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond</span></a> buyers, certification serves an even greater role, verifying not only the diamond’s properties but also its ethical and sustainable origins.</p>",
            "custom_id": "certification"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding IGI Diamond Certification — Global Trust Meets Innovation",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding IGI Diamond Certification — Global Trust Meets Innovation</h2>",
            "custom_id": "igi"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iCrgtC": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IGI_1080_680.png",
            "text": "<p>The IGI (International Gemological Institute) is one of the world’s most respected names in diamond grading and gemstone certification. Known for its consistency and technological advancement, IGI provides grading reports for both natural and lab grown diamonds.</p><p>An IGI diamond certification covers critical aspects such as carat weight, color grade, clarity, proportions, polish, symmetry, and any inclusions or treatments. The report also includes a unique laser inscription number that corresponds to the certificate, ensuring full traceability.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cRqJfQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>IGI’s expertise in grading lab grown diamonds has made it the preferred certification partner for ethical jewelry brands worldwide. For example, at Lucira Jewelry, every lab grown diamond is IGI-certified — offering complete assurance of quality and authenticity. This partnership reflects a shared commitment to sustainability and transparent luxury.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Verify a Diamond Certificate",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Verify a Diamond Certificate</h2><p>Verifying your diamond certificate is an essential step to ensure authenticity and protect your investment. Here’s how you can do it:</p>",
            "custom_id": "importance"
          }
        },
        "image_6ydz87": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Verify_a_Diamond_Certificate_1080_300.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_wMK4Ux": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ol><li>Check the Certificate Number – Every certificate includes a unique number, often inscribed on the diamond’s girdle.<br/></li><li>Visit the Official Website – For IGI, visit igi.org. Enter the report number to access the certificate details.<br/></li><li>Cross-Verify with Physical Characteristics – Match the carat weight, color, and clarity mentioned in the report with the diamond’s description.<br/></li><li>Look for the Laboratory Logo and Signature – Authentic certificates carry the official logo, security features, and authorized signatures.<br/></li></ol><p>Lucira’s certified diamonds, including<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> 1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a> pieces, always include a verifiable IGI report, allowing you to validate every detail before purchase.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Diamond Certification",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Diamond Certification in India — What Buyers Should Know</h2><p>India has emerged as a global hub for diamond cutting, polishing, and now, lab grown diamond innovation. With this growth comes an increasing emphasis on reliable diamond certification in India.</p><p>Indian buyers can obtain certificates from internationally recognized bodies such as IGI India, SGL (Solitaire Gemological Laboratories), and GIA India. These organizations follow stringent global standards, providing detailed reports on the diamond’s quality and authenticity.</p><p>When purchasing a diamond in India:</p><ul><li>Always request an official certification report<br/><br/></li><li>Verify the report number on the laboratory’s website<br/><br/></li><li>Check for laser inscriptions that match the certificate<br/><br/></li><li>Purchase only from trusted retailers like Lucira Jewelry, which guarantee certified, conflict-free diamonds<br/><br/></li></ul><p>For lab grown diamonds, India’s growing infrastructure ensures that certifications align with international benchmarks, reinforcing trust and transparency in the market.</p>",
            "custom_id": "components"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AWtNat": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Why Lucira Jewelry Trusts IGI Certification",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Why Lucira Jewelry Trusts IGI Certification</h2><p>At Lucira Jewelry, every diamond is a symbol of integrity, elegance, and innovation. The brand exclusively partners with IGI for certification, ensuring that each diamond meets the highest standards of quality and ethics.</p><p>Lucira’s designs combine IGI-certified<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond jewellery</span></a> with expert craftsmanship, offering jewelry that embodies purity, responsibility, and beauty. From solitaire engagement rings to modern mangalsutras, each piece comes with an assurance of authenticity and a legacy of trust.<br/><br/></p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Certified Brilliance ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Certified Brilliance That Reflects Your Values</h2><p>A diamond certification is more than a report; it is a guarantee of trust. Whether you’re purchasing a natural diamond or choosing a sustainable lab grown diamond, certification ensures that your jewelry stands for honesty, quality, and ethical brilliance.</p><p>As India’s leading lab grown diamond brand, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a> is proud to offer only IGI-certified diamonds, crafted to celebrate your milestones with confidence and conscience. When you choose Lucira, you’re not just buying jewelry — you’re investing in authenticity.</p><p>Shop IGI-certified<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond jewellery</span></a>, rings,<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-earrings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> earrings</span></a>, and<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> necklaces</span></a> with Lucira Jewelry. Experience certified brilliance with India’s most trusted ethical jewelry brand.<br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "check"
          }
        }
      },
